# @codefast/cli

- **Canonical doc:** **[`packages/cli/ARCHITECTURE.md`](packages/cli/ARCHITECTURE.md)** тАФ layout (`bin`, `cli`, `core`, `config`, `arrange`, `mirror`, `tag`), boundaries, `#/` imports, naming (`SPEC.md`).
- **Style:** Commander argv, `Result` / `AppError`, plain functions тАФ avoid introducing DI containers or hexagonal ceremony here.
- **Domain:** Keep **`*/domain/**`** pure (no Commander, `process`, or ad hoc logging); I/O at edges or in `core/`.
- **Tests:** Under **`packages/cli/tests/`** only (Vitest, Node).

When editing CLI, open or `@`-mention **`packages/cli/ARCHITECTURE.md`** at the start of the task.
